# CloakRadar

**Advanced Traffic Cloaking & Bot Detection Platform**

> Advertise anything. Anywhere. Without bans.

🔗 **[cloakradar.pro](https://cloakradar.pro)**

---

## What is CloakRadar?

CloakRadar is an all-in-one traffic cloaking and tracking platform built for affiliate marketers and media buyers. It combines enterprise-grade cloaking with a full tracking suite, eliminating the need for separate tools like Voluum for tracking and standalone cloakers for ad protection.

Whether you're running campaigns on Facebook, Google, TikTok, or native ad networks, CloakRadar keeps your campaigns live by intelligently filtering bot traffic, moderators, and compliance checkers — while giving you complete visibility into your click and conversion data.

---

## Key Features

### Bulletproof Cloaking

Reliably cloaks all major advertising platforms including Google, Facebook, TikTok, Bing, Snapchat, Taboola, Outbrain, MGID, and many more. Moderators and review bots see a compliant safe page while real users are routed to your actual offer.

### Full Tracking Suite

Complete click and conversion tracking with S2S (server-to-server) postbacks, multi-step funnels, A/B split testing, and real-time analytics. CloakRadar is designed to fully replace dedicated trackers like Voluum.

### Checker Bot Protection

Blocks all major website checkers and security scanners including Google Safe Browsing, VirusTotal, Kaspersky, BrandVerity, GeoEdge, AdSecure, and The Media Trust. Your landing pages stay clean in the eyes of automated compliance tools.

### JA3/JA4 TLS Fingerprinting

Advanced TLS fingerprinting technology that detects headless browsers, Selenium, Puppeteer, Playwright, and other automation tools that traditional cloakers miss entirely. This provides a detection layer that goes beyond IP and user-agent filtering.

### Behavioral Analysis

Analyzes visitor behavior patterns to distinguish between real human traffic and sophisticated bots that mimic human browsing. This adds another layer of protection against advanced detection methods.

### Click Fraud Detection

Identifies and filters fraudulent clicks, protecting your ad spend from being wasted on bot traffic. Generate fraud refund reports as evidence to recover wasted ad spend from traffic sources.

### Spy Tool Blocker

Hides your campaigns and landing pages from competitive intelligence tools like AdSpy, BigSpy, and other spy platforms. Keep your winning campaigns private.

---

## How It Works

1. **Create a Campaign** — Set up your campaign in the CloakRadar dashboard with your traffic source, safe page, and offer page.
2. **Configure Filters** — Choose your cloaking rules: bot detection, VPN/proxy filtering, geo-targeting, JA3/JA4 fingerprinting, and behavioral analysis.
3. **Deploy Your Link** — Use the CloakRadar campaign URL in your ads. All traffic passes through CloakRadar's edge servers.
4. **Automatic Filtering** — Bots, moderators, and checkers see your safe page. Real human visitors are routed to your offer with sub-5ms latency.
5. **Track Everything** — Monitor clicks, conversions, revenue, and ROI in real-time with full funnel analytics.

