## Performance

- **99.9% Detection Rate** — Multi-layer detection catches bots that single-method cloakers miss.
- **< 5ms Response Time** — Lightning-fast redirects powered by global edge servers. Your visitors won't notice any delay.
- **Global Infrastructure** — Edge servers distributed worldwide for low-latency filtering regardless of your traffic's geographic origin.

